@startuml

title frontend アーキテクチャ構造図

top to bottom direction
hide methods
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 40
skinparam ranksep 80
skinparam ArrowFontSize 10

skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #f7f9fc
    BorderColor #546e7a
    FontColor #243447
}
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor #ffffff
    BorderColor #546e7a
    FontColor #243447
}

package "Frontend Bootstrap" as BootstrapLayer {
    class "Frontend Bootstrap" as FrontendBootstrap {
        + entrypoint で gateway を生成する
        + root view へ注入する
    }
}

package "View" as ViewLayer {
    class "View" as View {
        + 画面を表示する
        + DOM event を controller へ渡す
    }
}

package "ScreenController" as ScreenControllerLayer {
    class "ScreenController" as ScreenController {
        + screen local な依存を束ねる
        + UseCase を起動する
        + Presenter で view model を返す
    }
}

package "Frontend UseCase" as FrontendUseCaseLayer {
    class "Frontend UseCase" as FrontendUseCase {
        + 画面更新手順を決める
        + GatewayContract と Store を使う
    }

    class "GatewayContract" as GatewayContract {
        + usecase 依存境界
    }

    FrontendUseCase -[hidden]down-> GatewayContract
}

package "Presenter と Store" as PresenterStoreLayer {
    class "Store" as Store {
        + screen state の正本を保持する
    }

    class "Presenter" as Presenter {
        + state を view model へ整形する
    }

    Store -[hidden]right-> Presenter
}

package "Gateway と RuntimeEventAdapter" as TransportAdapterLayer {
    package "Gateway" as GatewayAdapterGroup {
        class "Gateway" as WailsGateway {
            + backend Bind を呼ぶ
            + DTO 変換を閉じ込める
        }

        class "GatewayDTO" as GatewayDto {
            + request / response DTO
        }

        class "generated wailsjs" as WailsJs {
            + backend 呼び出し wrapper
        }

        WailsGateway -[hidden]down-> GatewayDto
        GatewayDto -[hidden]right-> WailsJs
    }

    package "RuntimeEventAdapter" as RuntimeAdapterGroup {
        class "RuntimeEventAdapter" as RuntimeEventAdapter {
            + Wails event を購読する
            + screen handler へ写像する
        }

        class "Wails Runtime" as WailsRuntime {
            + push event を配信する
        }

        RuntimeEventAdapter -[hidden]down-> WailsRuntime
    }

    GatewayAdapterGroup -[hidden]right-> RuntimeAdapterGroup
}

FrontendBootstrap --> View : gateway を渡す

View --> ScreenController : 操作を渡す
ScreenController --> FrontendUseCase : 起動する
ScreenController --> Store : 状態を購読する
ScreenController --> Presenter : view model を組み立てる

FrontendUseCase --> GatewayContract : 依存する
FrontendUseCase --> Store : 状態を更新する
GatewayContract --> WailsGateway : 実装する
WailsGateway --> GatewayDto : DTO を使う
WailsGateway --> WailsJs : Bind を呼ぶ

RuntimeEventAdapter --> WailsRuntime : event を購読する

BootstrapLayer -[hidden]down-> ViewLayer
ViewLayer -[hidden]down-> ScreenControllerLayer
ScreenControllerLayer -[hidden]down-> FrontendUseCaseLayer
FrontendUseCaseLayer -[hidden]down-> PresenterStoreLayer
PresenterStoreLayer -[hidden]down-> TransportAdapterLayer

FrontendBootstrap -[hidden]down-> View
View -[hidden]down-> ScreenController
ScreenController -[hidden]down-> FrontendUseCase
FrontendUseCase -[hidden]down-> WailsGateway

legend bottom
    architecture.md の構造主語と節名に合わせる。
    層をまたぐ主依存は上から下に読む。
    RuntimeEventAdapter の handler / store 更新線は見やすさのため要約する。
endlegend

@enduml
